quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,"Sabu woowde Quraysi en e aadorde Й“e."
  106,2,"Й—atngal dabbunde faade Yaman e ceeЙ—u faade Saam tawa hoЙ“e kisi."
  106,3,"Yo Й“e ndew jom ndu suudu hormaandu Kanko tan, Oon newnanЙ—o Й“e ngal Й—atngal, woto Й“e ndenndi Mbo e goЙ—Й—o."
  106,4,"Oon ГұamminЙ—o Й“e saanga heege, o hoolniЙ“e e kulol, ko laati e Й“erЙ—e arab teddinde suudu hormaandu ndu e teddinde hoЙ—Й“e heen."
  107,1,"Mbela A anndii oon fennoowo njoЙ“di Гұande darnga."
  107,2,"Oon woni duГұiroowo alyatiime e mbaadi cattundi."
  107,3,"O reerЙ—atah e Гұamminde miskiin o reerЙ—inirtah goЙ—Й—o Гұamminde miskiin."
  107,4,"Halkude e leptude Й“een welsandiiЙ“e nder juulde mum en, Й“e ngoЖҙaako nde haa waktu hende yawta."
  107,5,""
  107,6,"Й“een waЙ—ooЙ“e yiingo e golle mum en e juulde mum en, Й“e cellintah golle ngam Alla."
  107,7,"HoЙ“e kaЙ—a wallude tanaa mum en ko lorla alah e wallirde Й“e Й—uum."
  108,1,"Min tottiima-aan nelaaЙ—o- moЖҙЖҙere heewnde, ina hende caatngol Alkawsara ka aljanna."
  108,2,"Yettu Alla e o neema, nde njuulantaa Mbo Kanko gooto kirsa, ko luuri no sirkuЙ“e mbaЙ—ata Й—uum woni Й“allaraade Alla sanamuuji."
  108,3,"Oon gaГұЙ—o ma woni taЖҙiiЙ—o e kala moЖҙЖҙe bonЙ—o mbo annduЙ—a si haalaama ko bone tan haalate e mum."